{"tid":1519680,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"老野講兩句","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:46:46.000Z","uid":276838,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d226340a9cde5feb55c8e45a500e486f677113e7","tid":1519680,"uid":276838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:34:55.000Z","msg":"西環治港就緊架啦，呢兩日POPO既行動，兩個字，戇鳩。<br />\n<br />\n只有西環呢班官先會以為拉晒所謂頭面人物會搞掂件事。仲戇鳩。<br />\n<br />\n共產黨唔想發生既事，佢永遠都唔會發生，如果聽日有任何一件魔物開槍，無論死傷，（手足唔好有事呀）一定要出報告，如果係班內地炒散開既咁佢地就仆街。而且開左槍傷人，咁外媒就真係可以大做文章，無論件事邊個喏，佢都一定做你，佢想搞老共嘛。<br />\n<br />\n香港既籌碼由頭到尾都無變過，大家雖然係雞蛋對高牆，但我地係金蛋。所以，唔好太消沉。<br />\n<br />\n呢場仗，有排打，大家加油。<br />\n<br />\n只有眼前路，沒有身後身<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n林鄭必亡"},{"pid":"f95bfd333e08b92cab973fec8e652500b2ff68d8","tid":1519680,"uid":1102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"不被捕不受傷"},{"pid":"6d201df9c665654058cdc73b0579c3c261730f54","tid":1519680,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:36:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0dab2adeef70000edb24c275c6b4e861f1023177","tid":1519680,"uid":143321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h9huftP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9huftP.jpg&h=ef6d336f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d03d16d2aba402d25480dcb284e7239ba7927c53","tid":1519680,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:38:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"831780ea347a1c2598136480017260cebfccc69f","tid":1519680,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:39:12.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd